                    "We build substitution engines that learn individual preferences. A customer who previously accepted organic alternatives but rejected conventional ones gets organic suggestions first. A customer who always buys the same brand gets brand-matched alternatives. The system presents options ranked by predicted acceptance probability, and pickers can request real-time approval via push notification for edge cases. Acceptance rates climb from the industry average of 50-60% to 85%+ within 3 months of deployment."
